### 社区模块 — 点赞 / 收藏 / 评论 / 标签

### @name toggleLike
POST {{baseUrl}}/likes/{{screenplayId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### @name getLikeStatus
GET {{baseUrl}}/likes/{{screenplayId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### @name toggleFavorite
POST {{baseUrl}}/favorites/{{screenplayId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### @name getFavoriteStatus
GET {{baseUrl}}/favorites/{{screenplayId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### @name listComments
GET {{baseUrl}}/comments/{{screenplayId}}?page=1&page_size=20
Accept: application/json

###

### @name createComment
POST {{baseUrl}}/comments/{{screenplayId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "parent_id": 0,
  "content": "很棒的剧本！"
}

###

### @name createReply
POST {{baseUrl}}/comments/{{screenplayId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "parent_id": 1,
  "content": "同意，构图很棒。"
}

###

### @name listTags
GET {{baseUrl}}/tags?namespace=default
Accept: application/json

###

### @name createTag
POST {{baseUrl}}/tags
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "namespace": "default",
  "name": "Cosplay",
  "slug": "cosplay"
}

###

### @name tagScreenplay
POST {{baseUrl}}/tags/{{screenplayId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tag_id": 1
}

###

### @name untagScreenplay
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/tags/{{screenplayId}}/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### @name listReplies
GET {{baseUrl}}/comments/{{screenplayId}}/replies/1?page=1&page_size=20
Accept: application/json
